quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  27,83,"Yaye ngaloo Mini xa Siya kubaqokelela kwisizwe ngasinye, iqela labo babephika iiVesi zeThu liya kuqhutywa luyimikrozo"
  27,84,"Bade baye kufika kwindawo yoMgwebo, Aze Athi (uAllâh): “Nayiphika na nina imiqondiso yaM lo gama naningayiqiqi elwazini (lwenu) kanti yintoni kanye le naniyenza?”"
  27,85,"Lize iLizwi lizaliseke kubo, ngokuba benza ubugwenxa, yaye abayi (kukwazi) ukuthetha"
  27,86,Ababoni na bona ukuba Senza ubusuku khona ukuze baphumle ngabo nemini ebanika ukubona? Inene kuko oku kukho imiqondiso kubantu abakholwayo
  27,87,"NgeMini ekuya kuvuthelwa iXilongo ngayo, yaye wonke osezulwini naye wonke osemhlabeni uya kunkwantya ngaphandle kwabo uAllâh Aya kuthanda (ukuba bangoyiki). Yaye bonke baza kuza kuYe bethobekile"
  27,88,"Ke kaloku uzibona iintaba uzicingele ukuba ziqinile, lo gama ziya kudlula njengokudlula kwamafu. Ngumsebenzi ka-Allâh, Owafezekisa izinto zonke. Inene Yena Unolwazi ngoko nikwenzayo"
  27,89,"Nabani na lowo uya kuza nesenzo esilungileyo (ngeMini yoMgwebo), uya kufumana umvuzo ongcono kunaso (isenzo eso) yaye bona (abanjalo) kuloyiko lwaloo Mini baya kukhuseleka"
  27,90,Kananjalo nabani na oya kuza nesenzo esikukungcola ubuso babo (banjalo) buya kujulelwa ezantsi eMlilweni. (Kuze kuthiwe) Ingaba nihlawulelwe enye into ngaphandle koko nanidla ngokukwenza na?”
  27,91,"(Yithi Muhammad): “Mna ndiyalelwe kuphela ukuba ndinqule iNkosi yesi sixeko, Eyasenza saNgcwele ekuyiYo ezizezaYo izinto zonke. Yaye kananjalo ndiyalelwe ukuba ndibe ngomnye wamaMuslim"
  27,92,"Nokuba ndicengceleze i’Kur’ân. Nabani na ke okhokelweyo yena ukhokelelwe inzuzo yakhe kuphela; kwaye nabani na lowo ulahlekayo yithi (kuye), “Kuphela mna ndingomnye wabalumkisi.”"
  27,93,"Kananjalo yithi: “Iindumiso zonke mazibe kuAllâh. Yena Uya kunibonisa imiqondiso yaKhe, yaye niya kuyazi. Kananjalo iNkosi yenu akungaba Ayikwazi enikwenzayo.”"